    </div>
    
    <div class="quick_link" id="feed_link">
      Stay up to date easily with the <a href="feed:http://github.com/jlnr/gosu/commits/master.atom">RSS feed from GitHub</a>, or subscribe even to Gosu news and discussion easily via the <a href="http://www.libgosu.org/cgi-bin/mwf/forum_feeds.pl">feeds from the forum</a>.
